SUMMARY:Awaken Joy: Changing Timelines to Leave Negative Realities
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nHow’s your joy d
 oing these days? Don’t worry if you’re scared or in despair\, as many 
 people are. Yes\, some scary folks want to end the world because they inco
 nsistently believe that destruction will somehow save them\, but their fal
 se choices don’t have to affect you. They want you to believe that they 
 have powers over you\, but heck they can’t run their own life much less 
 run yours. You really do have all the power that you need to choose a happ
 y healthy future for yourself\, even if you don’t yet understand how tha
 t works. Just keep asking for solutions and responding to the opportunitie
 s that come your way. If you want to set yourself free with higher guidanc
 e\, join us this Sunday March 22\, 2026 for a free empowering talk on the 
 new hugely positive world that is dawning just for you.\n\nThis is not a t
 rick or gimmick. It’s really very simple. The Universe is alive and it l
 oves you. It knows how to thrive and wants to share with you every solutio
 n that you’ll ever need to live happily ever after. You’re a vital bel
 oved form of the Universe\, so of course it wants you to be healthy and ha
 ppy within it. Just as you would want every part of your body to be health
 y within you. Nature has given you a human body that’s miraculous in its
  abilities to function\, heal\, and grow. The Universe is fully capable of
  everything you’ll ever need to live in joy forever.\n\nForever? Yes for
 ever. But how does the Universe know with full confidence that every probl
 em will have a solution? Aha\, you’re worried from the human perspective
  of time and space that says some things do not yet exist. Time can seem s
 cary when you don’t understand how time really works. False negative bel
 iefs say the future is unknown\, unmade\, and hard to control. False belie
 fs say that time is your enemy\, as it separates you from what you once ha
 d that you loved\, until you can only mourn its loss.\n\nFalse beliefs say
  that when you luck into a happy moment\, now the work has just begun to k
 eep that happiness. You must protect your good fortune\, build a vision\, 
 and convince other people to cooperate with you. None of this is true\, bu
 t the stress you feel is typical of false beliefs that tell a scary lie an
 d then make you hold onto that lie in order to fix it. But you can never f
 ix a lie\, because you can’t make true what’s never true. You can only
  disbelieve a lie and switch to working with what always worked. Work with
  the truths that are always true for you.\n\nTime is NOT to build the phys
 ical world. The origins of the physical world are not physical\, so time c
 an’t make or break anything. Time is just the order in which you underst
 and what always exists eternally in the infinite multiverse of everything 
 coexistent. You hold a book in your hands and it’s all there right now\,
  yes? The images of the story are organized in words\, gathered into chapt
 ers that you can re-experience in sequence whenever you choose. That’s w
 hat time is like\, a pre-written story to enjoy.\n\nIt’s been over a cen
 tury since Einstein in 1905 showed that time and space are not separate\, 
 that they are somehow interconnect so past and future are simultaneous. Qu
 antum physics has long said that the physical world is best understood as 
 limited local experiences of eternal infinite quantum fields of energy pot
 entials. In other words\, relax! Everything you’ll ever need is always a
 vailable. Just let higher dimensional friends lead you to the best solutio
 ns that you need when you need them. Divine timing is the time in which yo
 u lose nothing and gain everything. All your best life moments are portals
  to explore and grow in joy forever.\n\nFor this meetup\, recall your chil
 dhood dreams that never die and your heart that loves without end. Are you
  ready to let your mind relax so it can learn new better ways to live? Man
 y people are resistant to the miracles of the living loving Universe becau
 se they were burned on the lies of old false paradigms. Well of course lie
 s hurt\, that’s what makes them lies\, so are you going to stay stuck on
  them? The old false world is dying with folks who still think that war ma
 kes peace and other impossibilities. Let them go so you can go where you p
 refer. Getting your preferences will give you joy\, while your needs will 
 make you happy. You are human\, and what human beings need is a safe path 
 to reach a life of joy! I’ll explain the path to freedom that my soul ha
 s been teaching me\, and how it can work for you as well. Let all people b
 e examples of how they run their own Universe\, as your higher dimensional
  self leads you into the best timelines for you.\n\nWelcome! Our Inner Sel
 ves Mastery spiritual support group is free online every Sunday 11am-130pm
  EDT\, with the last 30 minutes for a guided meditation. If you can’t st
 ay you can get the recording. You can signup here for this meeting and vis
 it www.signupISM.com for all events\, newsletter\, videos\, and more.\n\nB
 est wishes\,\nCarl Johann Schroeder\nInner Selves Mastery\nspiritual teach
 ing and coaching\nquick-links at [www.signupISM.com](http://www.signupISM.
 com)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/raleigh-triangle-activities/events/31
 3881483/
