SUMMARY:Dinner at Bronco Tacos 
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\n**Dinner at Bronco
  Taco’s**\n\nWhere: **Bronco Tacos\, 3434 Edwards Mill Rd\, Unit 11\, Ra
 leigh\, NC 27612 (919) 594-1719**\n**https://broncotacosnc.com/home/**\nWh
 en: **Saturday March 28th\, 7pm**\nBronco Tacos is a lively Mexican eatery
  where bold flavors and fresh ingredients collide to create unforgettable 
 dishes that ignite the taste buds. From sizzling fajitas to handcrafted ta
 cos bursting with authenticity\, Bronco Tacos invites diners on a flavorfu
 l journey through the heart of Mexico. So\, let’s go give it a try later
  this month and try it for ourselves!\nOrganizer: Dwen Andrews 919 624 076
 2/ 919 244 2710 [dwencita@gmail.com](mailto:dwencita@gmail.com) LE2605
